text: Dolichostyrax longipes is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1913 and is known from Borneo.BioLib.cz - Dolichostyrax longipes. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Cerambycidae
